entries.journal_entry_description: Aja Sen, the doctor on the Tansarii space station has asked you to gather DNA from the Rak'qua guards of Station Gamma.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Either use the Gamma Shuttle system, or fly your own space craft.
entries.task00_journal_entry_title: Travel to Station Gamma Via the Shuttle or Your Ship
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Your mission for Aja Sen is completed. Return to Tansarii space station to talk to her.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Return to Aja with the Blood samples you have taken.
entries.task03_journal_entry_title: Return to Aja Sen in the Medical Center
entries.task05_journal_entry_description: Gather blood samples from Rak'qua Pistoleers.
entries.task05_journal_entry_title: Kill Rak'qua Pistoleers in Station Gamma
entries.task06_journal_entry_description: Gather blood samples from Rak'qua Shamans.
entries.task06_journal_entry_title: Kill Rak'qua Shamans in Station Gamma
entries.task07_journal_entry_description: Gather blood samples from Rak'qua Warriors.
entries.task07_journal_entry_title: Kill Rak'qua Warriors in Station Gamma
